reviewText:
This game was good some years ago, now is just.. outdated!
I tried the game just for fun and the nostalgia since i played back in the days this game was good.
Pros:
- Alot of classes;
- Can play all the classes with one character only;
- Can play more than 1 class at same which means you can create your own play style;
- Pets that can evolve;

Cons:
- Hotkeys sucks, honestly the only hotbar with hotkeys is the first one and is F1, F2, etc, can't change;
- 100% grind;
- Outdated graphics;
- Low amount of content comparing to other games;
- Resolution issues, i had to go directly to the files to change the resolution;
- Overall just an outdated game!

Im not saying the game is bad because it isn't but comparing to the games we see out there.. you know, this one can't compete with them, end of story.

I recommend this game?
Thats a hard question because i think you should try the game if you have nothing better to do and see by yourself but im not sure if it will be worth your time if you are playing current mmos.. like i said, give it a shot if you are bored and have nothing else to do!
